21 HIGHEST NUMBER OF TOTAL VOTES IN THE ELECTION ELECTED TO A TERM OF FOUR
22 YEARS, WITH THE ELECTION FOR EACH SENATE SEAT HELD AGAIN IN TWO
23 THOUSAND AND THIRTY–SIX AND EVERY FOUR YEARS THEREAFTER.
